---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="New Construction Plumbing | Berkeley Plumbing — Conejo Valley, CA"
  description="C-36 licensed new construction plumbing in the Conejo Valley. Berkeley Plumbing works directly with general contractors and design teams on custom homes, ADUs, and multi-unit builds. CSLB #1115151."
>

  <!-- Page hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy-900 text-white py-16 lg:py-24 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <a href="/" class="text-copper text-sm hover:text-copper-light mb-6 inline-block">← Back to home</a>
      <p class="text-copper font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Services</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-5">New Construction Plumbing</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        Full rough-in to finish for custom homes, ADUs, and multi-unit residential builds in the Conejo Valley. Working directly from architectural plans alongside your general contractor and design team.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

      <!-- Main content -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">Built from the Plans Up</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          New construction plumbing requires a plumber who can read architectural and structural drawings, coordinate with other trades, and sequence work so the project doesn't stall. Berkeley Plumbing brings that skill set to every new build in the Conejo Valley, from custom single-family homes in Westlake Village to ADUs in Newbury Park.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          I work directly with general contractors, design-build firms, and custom home builders. Every rough-in is installed with the finish in mind: correct fixture placement, proper venting, and code-compliant layout that passes California inspection on the first visit.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mt-8">What's Included</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Complete rough-in: supply, drain, waste, and vent systems</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Fixture setting and finish plumbing</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Water heater installation (tankless or traditional)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Gas line installation and pressure testing</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Plan review and coordination with GC and design team</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> City and county permit coordination</li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-copper mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Final inspection walk-through</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mt-8">Working with General Contractors</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Subcontractor reliability is one of the most common pain points on new construction projects. Berkeley Plumbing operates as a professional trade partner: I show up when scheduled, communicate clearly, and don't create delays for other trades. If something on the plans needs clarification before rough-in, I'll flag it before it becomes a change order.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          I've worked on custom homes and larger residential projects throughout Newbury Park, Agoura Hills, Thousand Oaks, Westlake Village, and Calabasas. If you're a GC looking for a reliable plumbing sub for an upcoming build, reach out before the permit is pulled.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="bg-stone-warm rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100 sticky top-24">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-900 mb-4">Request an Estimate</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-5 leading-relaxed">
            Describe your project and I'll provide upfront pricing before any work begins.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="block w-full bg-copper hover:bg-copper-light text-white font-semibold py-3 px-5 rounded text-center transition-colors mb-3"
          >
            Get an Estimate
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:(310) 733-7808"
            class="block w-full border border-slate-300 hover:border-navy-800 text-slate-700 font-semibold py-3 px-5 rounded text-center transition-colors text-sm"
          >
            Call (310) 733-7808
          </a>

          <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> CSLB #1115151</p>
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> C-36 Licensed</p>
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Upfront pricing</p>
            <p class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-copper" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Code-compliant work</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service areas -->
  <section class="py-12 px-4 bg-stone-warm border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm text-center">
        New construction plumbing services in:
        <a href="/service-areas/newbury-park/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Newbury Park</a>,
        <a href="/service-areas/agoura-hills/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Agoura Hills</a>,
        <a href="/service-areas/thousand-oaks/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Thousand Oaks</a>,
        <a href="/service-areas/westlake-village/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Westlake Village</a>,
        <a href="/service-areas/calabasas/" class="text-copper hover:underline">Calabasas</a>, and surrounding communities.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
